{"serial": "41014", "department_serial": 40, "code": "BA4000", "class": "B", "name": {"en": "Business Policy", "ch": "企業政策"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Yi-chi, Hsiao"], "ch": ["蕭義棋"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["5", "6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "I", "room": "303"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 60, "department": {"ch": "企業管理學系", "en": "Department of Business Administration"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "全部使用", "en": "All"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 43, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程旨在幫助學生了解企業政策的基本理論與實務應用，培養學生在複雜商業環境中進行策略思考與決策的能力，並能夠分析與解釋不同策略選擇的潛在影響。", "en": "This course aims to provide students with a comprehensive understanding of the fundamental theories and practical applications of corporate policy, equipping them with the ability to engage in strategic thinking and decision-making in complex business environments, as well as analyze and interpret the potential impacts of different policy choices."}, "outline": {"ch": "企業政策級企業策略係統合企業內相關資源之整體性指導原則，和企業功能性之管理有極大的分野。本課程教授策略管理之程序，包括策略分析、策略形成與策略執行；亦即組織如何透過目標設定及進行一系列密切結合的行動與資源配置，俾能超越競爭對手的思維與手段。本課程包括策略思維的基本觀念、及如何在特定場域中競爭（競爭策略）與如何選擇場域（成長策略）等兩個層次。", "en": "Corporate policy and corporate strategy represent the comprehensive guiding principles for integrating various resources within an organization and are distinctly different from the management of functional areas. This course covers the process of strategic management, including strategic analysis, strategy formulation, and strategy implementation—essentially, how organizations set goals and carry out a series of closely aligned actions and resource allocations to surpass competitors in both thought and action. The course encompasses the fundamental concepts of strategic thinking and addresses two key levels: how to compete within a specific arena (competitive strategy) and how to select the appropriate arenas (growth strategy)."}, "textbook": {"ch": "參考書：湯明哲（2011）策略精論(基礎篇)、策略精論 (進階篇)，旗標出版社", "en": "參考書：Hill, Schilling and Jones (2017), Strategic Management, Theory, 12th ed. (華泰代理)"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "60", "en": "60"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "個案報告、文章導讀（組成績）40％\n期中與期末考試（二次，個人成績）40％\n課程參與（個人成績）20％", "en": "Case reports, HBR articles introduction (40％)\nMidterm ＆ Final (40％)\nParticipation (20％)"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "事前預約", "en": "By Appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "策略管理", "en": "策略管理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "管理知識", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "國際觀", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "永續發展", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "溝通能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Management Knowledge", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Critical Thinking and Problem-solving", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Global Perspective", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Sustainability Development", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Communication Skill", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam"]}]}, "assignCriteria": {"ch": ["系所:限企業管理學系。年級:限四年級。班別:限B。身份:限非交換生。指定課程:必須先修BA1003、先修BA2000、先修BA2030、先修BA3001、先修BA3005。"], "en": ["Department:Department of Business Administration only.Year:Fourth Year only.Class:B only.identity:Non-Exchange Students Only. Speci